Depends: xfontpath
Source: http://downloads.sourceforge.jp/mplus-fonts/5030/mplus_bitmap_fonts-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: a97a99acbee54976407dec828d03850c
Description: M+ BITMAP FONTS
